---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About"
  description="Kixlogic builds workforce intelligence software for life sciences organizations — biotech, pharma, medical device, and clinical research."
>
  <section class="about-page section">
    <div class="container about-inner">
      <div class="about-header">
        <span class="tag">About</span>
        <h1>Workforce intelligence<br />for life sciences</h1>
        <p class="about-lead">
          We started Kixlogic to solve a problem we kept seeing: specialized scientific talent is
          incredibly hard to find, evaluate, and pay competitively — and the tools available were
          built for everyone, which meant they were great for no one.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-section">
          <h2>What we build</h2>
          <p>
            Kixlogic Workforce Intelligence Platform is three products in one: an ATS purpose-built
            for scientific roles, a compensation intelligence module with life-sciences-specific
            benchmarks, and a sourcing engine that finds scientists who aren't on job boards.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every feature is built for the specific complexity of scientific hiring — niche skill sets,
            long time-to-fill cycles, highly competitive compensation, and candidate pools that are
            measured in hundreds, not thousands.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
          <h2>The bigger picture</h2>
          <p>
            Our long-term goal is simple: give every life sciences organization the same hiring and
            compensation intelligence that only the largest pharma and biotech companies currently
            have access to.
          </p>
          <p>
            We call it the Bloomberg Terminal for scientific talent. A single place to see who to hire,
            what to pay, where the talent exists, and how competitive your offers are — updated in
            real time, not published once a year in a PDF nobody reads.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-products">
        <h2>Our products</h2>
        <div class="products-list">
          <div class="pl-item">
            <div class="pl-icon teal">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#14B894" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M7 9h10M7 13h6" stroke="#14B894" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Kixlogic ATS</h3>
              <p>Applicant tracking, sourcing, and offer management for life sciences hiring teams.</p>
              <a href="/ats">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-item">
            <div class="pl-icon indigo">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M3 17l4-4 4 4 4-6 4 3" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Kixlogic Comp</h3>
              <p>Real-time compensation benchmarks, offer analysis, and workforce analytics for scientific roles.</p>
              <a href="/comp">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-item">
            <div class="pl-icon dim">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M3 9l9-6 9 6v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9z" stroke="#7ABFCC" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M9 22V12h6v10" stroke="#7ABFCC" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>ScientificGigs</h3>
              <p>Life sciences job board at scientificgigs.com. All Kixlogic WIP jobs syndicate here automatically.</p>
              <a href="https://scientificgigs.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit ScientificGigs →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-contact">
        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>Questions, partnership opportunities, or want a walkthrough? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:hello@kixlogic.com">hello@kixlogic.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
.about-page { padding-top: 5rem; }
.about-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }

.about-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
.about-header .tag { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.about-header h1 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.about-lead {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.about-section h2 {
  font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.about-section p { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }

.about-products { margin-bottom: 4rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.about-products h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.products-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
.pl-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}
.pl-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  border-radius: 11px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.pl-icon.teal   { background: var(--gold-dim); }
.pl-icon.indigo { background: var(--indigo-dim); }
.pl-icon.dim    { background: rgba(122,191,204,0.1); }
.pl-item h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.375rem; }
.pl-item p  { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.pl-item a  { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; transition: 0.2s; }
.pl-item a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

.about-contact h2  { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.about-contact p   { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
.about-contact a   { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
.about-contact a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
}
</style>
